{"tid":1965010,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"邊到有細裝嘅日本珍珠米賣？","createTime":"2020-04-09T08:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T09:52:34.000Z","uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d8947b143cadd3c5f1928bbc819f024dd9872389","tid":1965010,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T08:07:41.000Z","msg":"有冇係1kg以下嘅packing？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ddcb586ad765324b3842f52ebc08141b2f0607","tid":1965010,"uid":52240,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T08:15:55.000Z","msg":"我屌哂你哋老母 係咪光復左香港 五大訴求達到左啦？<br />\n做咩成個熱門都係食玩膠同睇女post？<br />\n如果呢個post上唔到熱門 冇哂行動post 我正式宣布呢個運動真係玩完 連登已死<br />\n連我個淺藍老母都問啲暴徒係咪搞完事 外國戰線著哂火咁大粒核彈都冇人理既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應承我 唔可以當手足係condom？<br />\n我哋揸住佢個春袋 呢粒核彈會令到中共好驚 手足就嚟贏 千祈唔可以中五毛分化撚嘅計 推走熱門行動Post 唔係我哋就嚟輸<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可 煲底見！"},{"pid":"1e6fbdad23bf1763512fe28b8b901cf9213fbb6f","tid":1965010,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b298504e66012aab779ed64384c08cd21b408d5","tid":1965010,"uid":165136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"sogo"},{"pid":"c72c8621f4cbc478b95f9608156b6c8ff555f717","tid":1965010,"uid":172042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T09:26:08.000Z","msg":"得華御結咋喎"},{"pid":"efd187acde158c2dd870b2f826ab40bfdba4a933